reviews.review_text: first bootleg This was my first bootleg (cassette) that a friend gave me back in the 80's. It is one of my favs. Unfortunately, the cassette is getting old and I would like to download this file. How can I do this please help????

Best of 78 I find this show to be as good as any played in the 1970's.  Half step, franklin's tower then the second set just soars.  Since when did they open the second set in 78 with that kind of jamming.  Absolutely one the best of the year.  Hear it.

If I had the world to give Set 2
Band presses on under all kinda circumstances.
The free form jams real interesting, studio feel
Jack a Roe comes like a freight train out of nowhere
Playing dissolves> Shakedown funky
This is really prime Dead
Just some board drop-outs especially late
but pretend you had to get a beer or something
WTG is Garcia at his most vulnerable.
